ts/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想落灘落唔到<br />\n<br />\nBtw著公褲當更好容易露蛋蛋"},{"pid":"3471d30c9c9975cea6b085342fec0ca47bfe0ab6","tid":342320,"uid":69939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T00:42:27.000Z","msg":"我都做過 最尾無renew到<br />\n<br />\n曾經番過一人池 <br />\n朝7am-10pm 番左一日無做<br />\n<br />\n又番過地獄池 X號銀X <br />\n講下野都唔得 又係番左一日無做"},{"pid":"9ab9366002f629dec9635d4cddafe278db3f4dda","tid":342320,"uid":73139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T01:10:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做緊康文池<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想落灘落唔到<br />\n<br />\nBtw著公褲當更好容易露蛋蛋</blockquote><br />\n公褲個內膽好安全喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80570f0a73e5a74dbe6e5635cbd2c214c4e11642","tid":342320,"uid":95413,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:09:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想入行有無指引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上網搵個拯溺班交幾千蚊報名  考完幾個章就做得<br />\n不過救生員就閪工黎  無人工加無晉升機會無野學無埋自己時間<br />\n撞正閪客閪池閪會所閪判頭重要受氣比人屌<br />\n<br />\n每3年要比幾百蚊renew一次章  <br />\n返頂更就好pay  可以成千蚊一日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n救生員同看更個分別如下<br />\n一個係泳池鳩曬同捐血餵蚊 另一個係大堂/商場冷氣地方行企坐<br />\n人工/時間用既其實相差唔多<br />\n看更有得升  做耐左好多人有20k up<br />\n老救做康文都有得升  不過要等上面d人死左先可以升  私池就唔好諗<br />\n看更一年四季有工開  老救夏天搵埋冬天糧 朝不保晚  四季池少之又少  同埋一到冬天就會減人工<br />\n看更準時有糧出  老救年年都有人比人拖糧/借d意扣糧<br />\n<br />\n想當救生員係長工咁返既巴打真係要三思<br />\n呢份工真係唔值得用咁多時間落去"},{"pid":"761c78c1d6f325ae208d1acf1986ff60a8b57690","tid":342320,"uid":54618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T11:34:00.000Z","msg":"全職咁翻左4個月之後 連頂更都冇興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e6bb71aa2d24b6c408a9d4fdcad40bf46d1e39","tid":342320,"uid":65593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T01:18:10.000Z","msg":"番緊啲hea尻有錢佬池 全日得一兩個人游 但人工低啲"},{"pid":"809f89fa91806c8375948c9cc08a1ee39fdbb163","tid":342320,"uid":107444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T09:40:15.000Z","msg":"反緊15個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日日攰撚到仆街"},{"pid":"1e168bda07c0358fb980f1251e842010010094b6","tid":342320,"uid":110453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:26:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做咗兩年 長鐘 <br />\n 唔想再覆修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一日十四個鐘 計埋坐車都十六個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 巴打唔會覺得辛苦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 諗緊仲做唔做落去好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一開始我都係番私家,十鳩幾個鐘番黎真係燃燒生命<br />\n依家撈緊康文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 公司仲調撚咗我去地獄池<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打7.5個鐘？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小弟上年番一日15.75個鍾"},{"pid":"665f5c8a56210e07ba603e454b146878d58a7743","tid":342320,"uid":110453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:28:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反緊15個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日日攰撚到仆街</blockquote><br />\n柯9地獄池？"},{"pid":"0f7fa723a4cd5b4ef926ed675f07f8f2ccf9c4ff","tid":342320,"uid":131264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:33:52.000Z","msg":"返開邊個池？講下邊個池最閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我教水都覺得有啲池同會所客極閪<br />\n有咩事就屌鳩啲救生員 明明唔關佢地事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27383e0eeb10d27abe8c16ea5e34d9a89dfa5054","tid":342320,"uid":88185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:45:58.000Z","msg":"多唔多女救生員？"},{"pid":"2f4bfa4020348e76ecc5945630ad24c052ee4814","tid":342320,"uid":5519,"l